sect3.para:
In the same way as in Individual Subscriptions, you will have the option to select
              from a list of existing users. Institutional Subscriptions cover entire organizations,
              but still must be *owned* by an individual account holder from your journal.

sect1.para:
In addition to managing the journal web site, the Journal Manager is also responsible
          for all of the user accounts in the system. From the Journal Manager's User Home page,
          you'll find the Users menu, which includes all possible user management options.
